languages.text: "Жаль, что твой народ не изволил издохнуть полностью вместе с вашей спесью".
"It is a shame that your kind did not die off entirely and spare the rest of us their arrogance."
languages.original_text: "Жаль, что твой народ не изволил издохнуть полностью вместе с вашей спесью".

traits.locale_text: "Shame that your people never considered going extinct and taking their blasted arrogance with them."

languages.text: “真遗憾，你的族人还没有死绝，我们还得继续忍受你们这股傲慢劲儿。”
languages.original_text: "It is a shame that your kind did not die off entirely and spare the rest of us their arrogance."

traits.locale_text: “真遗憾，要是你的族人全都死光了，连着他们那该死的傲慢一起消失，那该多好。”

languages.text: 「お前らが滅びず、我々がその傲慢さから免れなかったことは実に残念でならない」
languages.original_text: "It is a shame that your kind did not die off entirely and spare the rest of us their arrogance."

traits.locale_text: 「お前らが滅びず、我々がその傲慢さから免れなかったことは実に残念でならない」

languages.text: «Es una lástima que los suyos no se extinguieran por completo para librarnos a todos de su arrogancia».
languages.original_text: "It is a shame that your kind did not die off entirely and spare the rest of us their arrogance."

traits.locale_text: «Lástima que su gente nunca se planteara extinguirse y llevarse consigo su maldita arrogancia».

languages.text: "Es ist ein Jammer, dass Euer Volk nicht gänzlich ausgestorben ist und uns den Rest seiner Arroganz erspart hat."
languages.original_text: "It is a shame that your kind did not die off entirely and spare the rest of us their arrogance."

traits.locale_text: "Ein Jammer, dass Eure Spezies nie in Erwägung gezogen hat, einfach auszusterben und Eure verfluchte Arroganz mitzunehmen."

languages.text: « Quel dommage que votre peuple ne se soit pas simplement éteint pour nous épargner son arrogance ! »
languages.original_text: "It is a shame that your kind did not die off entirely and spare the rest of us their arrogance."

traits.locale_text: « Quel dommage que votre peuple n'ait jamais envisagé de tout simplement s'éteindre pour nous épargner son arrogance. »

languages.original_text: "It is a shame that your kind did not die off entirely and spare the rest of us their arrogance."
